  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span data-sheets-formula-bar-text-style=\"font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Arial';font-style:normal;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;\">Membership with NC's premiere (only) public transit solution. Trams are overcrowded, filthy, and barely functional. Primarily services the Rebuilding Urban Zones, with 2-3 stops in each. Does not extend to Pacifica. 1 stop in each Overpacked Suburb.</span></p><p>Can be purchased by-use for 10eb per trip - monthly membership is incurred alongside lifestyle expenses.</p><p><span data-sheets-formula-bar-text-style=\"font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Arial';font-style:normal;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;\">User suffers a -2 penalty to initiative rolls for arrival times when beginning scenes, except for Overpacked Suburb stops, which suffer -4. Using it to arrive in an unserviced district results in an initiative roll of 1. Possability of random encounters and pickpockets.</span></p>"
